<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/63000257/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Evaluation will be carried out progressively, through the submission of assignments during the course. At the end of the course, there will be a global exam of the whole subject. The assessment methodology will be the same for all students. The learning outcomes assessed will be RA16, RA17 and RA18.
If students fail to pass the course during the ordinary exam, they will have to take a comprehensive exam of the whole subject during the extraordinary exam. The learning outcomes assessed will be RA16, RA17 and RA18."""@es ;
